  "texts": [
    "In other words, the model's recurrent architecture inherently limits its ability to \"look back\" at previous tokens, as opposed to traditional self-attention mechanisms.",
    "While learned time decay helps prevent the loss of information, it is mechanistically limited compared to full selfattention.",
    "Another limitation of this work is the increased importance of prompt engineering in comparison to standard Transformer models.",
    "The linear attention mechanism used in RWKV limits the information from the prompt that will be carried over to the model's continuation.",
    "As a result, carefully designed prompts may be even more crucial for the model to perform well on tasks."
  ],
